<p><b>Thomas Jacob Hilfiger</b> (born March 24, 1951)<sup id="cite_ref-HELLOMAGAZINE_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-HELLOMAGAZINE-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> is an American fashion designer and founder of the premium lifestyle brand <a href="Tommy_Hilfiger_Corporation" title="Tommy Hilfiger Corporation">Tommy Hilfiger Corporation</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
